  <project_license>GPL-3.0-or-later</project_license>
  <name>SilkTex</name>
  <summary>LaTeX editor with live preview</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      SilkTex is a LaTeX editor designed for writing and compiling LaTeX documents
      with a focus on simplicity and productivity. It includes a live preview pane
      that shows the PDF output in real-time.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Clean, modern GTK4 interface with light and dark themes</li>
      <li>Syntax highlighting for LaTeX</li>
      <li>Real-time PDF preview</li>
      <li>Document structure navigation</li>
      <li>BibTeX support</li>
      <li>Document templates</li>
      <li>Snippets for quick code insertion</li>
      <li>Document statistics</li>
      <li>Error detection and highlighting</li>
      <li>Spell checking</li>
      <li>Project management for multiple files</li>
      <li>Multiple LaTeX engine support (pdflatex, xelatex, lualatex)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
